	(text "Characteristic impedance of transmission line\n(copper connection to IO) should be 90Ohms.\nEnsure that there is a large ground\npad underneath these resistors. \nResistors should be placed close to the IO.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 471.17 190.246 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "7ea42402-8b61-4b28-9df8-fb3e118307a3")
	)
	(text "Effective capacitance should be 10pF.\nSeries capacitance seen by the IO is\n15pF||15pF = 7.5pF. Add 3pF for estimated\nparasitic capacitance of the PCB. \n10.5 is close enough"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 325.374 51.054 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "96d7ea13-4a83-4616-b6c5-47fde89311c5")
	)
